mla'%20and%20raised%20questions%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20OBC%20reservation%20and%20implementation%20timeline.%20The%20Congress%20says%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20will%20not%20come%20into%20effect%20until%20after%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20law%20promises%20a%2033%25%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%2C%20but%20this%20may%20not%20come%20into%20force%20until%202029%2C%20NDTV%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20quota%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20first%20delimitation%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20after%20the%20bill%20becomes%20law%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20in%202027%2C%20since%20constituency%20redrawing%20only%20occurs%20after%20the%20next%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20is%20expected%20to%20introduce%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20to%20allow%20reservation%20in%20promotion%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20in%20government%20jobs.%20Mr%20Meghwal%20will%20also%20move%20the%20Advocates%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20amend%20the%20Advocates%20Act%2C%201961.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695177720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Fmb0sn5m8_sonia-gandhi-pti_625x300_14_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-reservation-bill-debate-today-sonia-gandhi-to-lead-congress-charge-4405761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20Chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20will%20lead%20the%20party's%20debate%20on%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-reservation-bill-debate