6-years-before-he-was-shot-nijjar-landed-in-canada-with-fake-papers%2Farticleshow%2F103795109.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20to%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20in%20India%20Is%20as%20Old%20as%20the%20Dharma%20Itself%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19154928%2Fabhijeet-gourav-jwr0xaXsYKk-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20weeks%20have%20passed%20since%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20sports%20minister%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fudhayanidhis-remarks-on-sanatana-dharma-triggers-political-row%2Farticle67267184.ece%5C%22%3Econdemned%20%3Cem%3Esanatan%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20vociferously%20and%20gave%20a%20call%20for%20its%20eradication%2C%20equating%20it%20to%20deadly%20infectious%20diseases.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20sensational%20statements%20routinely%20made%20by%20politicians%20that%20barely%20last%20a%20news%20cycle%2C%20this%20issue%20has%20lingered%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20original%20commentary%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-s-udhayanidhi-stalin-remains-defiant-over-controversial-sanatan-dharma-remark-says-ill-repeat-it-again-and-again-4359086%5C%22%3Estinging%20rebuke%20of%20a%20social%20evil%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20perpetrates%20inequality%20rather%20than%20a%20political%20attack%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20owning%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20throwing%20itself%20lock%2C%20stock%20and%20barrel%20into%20defending%20a%20dharma%20that%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20bedrock%20of%20Hinduism.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fudhayanidhi-remarks-require-proper-response-pm%2Farticle67277427.ece%5C%22%3Eexhort%20his%20ministers%20to%20give%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproper%20response%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20critique.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20observers%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fopinion%2Fdc-comment%2F160923%2Fdc-edit-india-bloc-wrong-both-on-sanatana-tv-anchor-ban.html%5C%22%3Efolly%20on%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20party%20DMK%20belongs%20to%2C%20as%20it%20gives%20electoral%20fodder%20to%20the%20Viswaguru%2C%20this%20in%20fact%20is%20an%20existential%20debate%20that%20has%20a%20lasting%20impact%20longer%20than%20any%20five-year%20election%20cycle%20because%20it%20impacts%20the%20millions%20that%20wallow%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20sanatan%20dharma%20knowingly%20or%20unknowingly%2C%20owing%20to%20their%20birth%20into%20a%20particular%20social%20order.%20It%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20India%20itself%2C%20as%20it%20has%20its%20origins%20in%20our%20history%20that%20pre-dates%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20dispensation%20might%20interpret%20this%20statement%20as%20a%20vindication%20of%20Bharat%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20the%20intent%20here.%20Sanatan%20dharma%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20its%20divisive%20and%20oppressive%20nature%20since%20time%20immemorial.%20To%20look%20at%20the%20long%20list%20of%20its%20critics%2C%20one%20has%20to%20start%20with%20Siddhartha%20Gautama%2C%20the%20Buddha%20himself.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital.sandiego.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1017%26context%3Dthrs-faculty%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520broke%2520with%2520tradition%2520by%2Crespected%2520as%2520leaders%2520in%2520society.%5C%22%3Eall-inclusive%20Sangha%20was%20born%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20rigid%20birth-based%20discriminatory%20caste%20system%20and%20subjugation%20of%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20proscribed%20by%20sanatana%20dharm.%20After%20Buddha%2C%20King%20Asoka%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20formidable%20foe%20to%20sanatan%20sharma%20%E2%80%93%20so%20much%20so%20that%20his%20ascent%20to%20the%20throne%20of%20the%20Magadha%20empire%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2FWhy-Hindutva-Loves-hate-Ashoka-Great%5C%22%3Eopposed%20tooth%20and%20nail%20by%20the%20sanatanis%20of%20the%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Historical%20books%20talk%20about%20multiple%20attempts%20on%20his%20life%20made%20by%20sacrificial%20Brahmins%20as%20he%20sought%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20ritualism%20and%20chose%20merit%20over%20birth-based%20hegemony.%20His%20embrace%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Findia%2Fbuddhism-was-india%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Emperor%2520Asoka%252C%2520the%2520Mauryan%2Csize%2520of%2520the%2520present%2520dome.%5C%22%3EBuddhism%20made%20it%20the%20predominant%20religion%20of%20the%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20sanatan%20dharma.%20This%20was%20dealt%20with%20with%20brute%20force%20in%20post-Asoka%20years%20by%20the%20sanatanis%20when%20the%20Mauryan%20dynasty%20was%20essentially%20ended%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrunicle.com%2Fpushyamitra-shunga-an-unsung-hero-who-preserved-the-vedic-culture-and-sanatana-dharma%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520only%2520wrong%2520Pushyamitra%2520did%2Ckilled%2520by%2520his%2520own%2520minister.%5C%22%3EPushyamitra%20Sunga%2C%20a%20Brahmin%20warrior%20who%20killed%20Brihadrath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20last%20Mauryan%20king%2C%20while%20being%20his%20commander-in-chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20RSS%20Chief%20Has%20Taken%20the%20Lead%20in%20Critiquing%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20Why%20Can't%20Opposition%20Follow%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmohan-bhagwat-rss-sanatan-dharma-caste%5C%22%3EThe%20RSS%20Chief%20Has%20Taken%20the%20Lead%20in%20Critiquing%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20Why%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Opposition%20Follow%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20sanatan%20dharma%20flourished%20again%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Buddhism%2C%20a%20religion%20that%20was%20embraced%20by%20every%20country%20that%20it%20touched%20east%20of%20India%20but%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20mere%20shadow%20of%20its%20former%20glory%20days%20in%20its%20birthplace.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehimalayantimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fbuddhism-in-india-its-rise-fall-and-rise-again%5C%22%3Esystematic%20violent%20pogrom%20perpetrated%20by%20Pushyamitra%20was%20behind%20this%20relegation%20of%20Buddhism%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20annals%20of%20history%20in%20India.%20Thus%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianculturalforum.in%2F2019%2F02%2F16%2Fthe-history-of-india-is-a-history-of-mortal-conflict-between-buddhism-and-brahmanism%2F%5C%22%3Erightly%20pointed%20out%20by%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20history%20of%20India%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20history%20of%20mortal%20conflict%20between%20Buddhism%20and%20Brahmanism.%E2%80%9D%20But%20opposition%20to%20sanatan%20dharma%20did%20not%20die%20down%20with%20the%20elimination%20of%20Buddhism%20from%20India.%20A%20long%20line%20of%20thinkers%20and%20proponents%20of%20equality%20and%20social%20justice%20emerged%20from%20varied%20places%20in%20the%20landmass%20of%20India%20at%20different%20time%20points%20in%20history.%20To%20name%20a%20few%20prominent%20figures%20among%20them%2C%20Kabir%2C%20Basavanna%2C%20Akka%20Mahadevi%2C%20Narayana%20guru%2C%20Jyothirao%20Phule%2C%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20Periyar%20and%20Ambedkar%20all%20rallied%20against%20the%20injustice%20that%20is%20inherent%20to%20sanatan%20dharma%20in%20their%20own%20might.%20This%20brief%20historical%20perspective%20proves%20it%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20critique%20and%20opposition%20to%20sanatan%20dharma%20is%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20India%20as%20this%20dharma%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%20has%20been%20clear%20about%20his%20stance%20%E2%80%93%20he%20opposes%20sanatan%20dharma%20because%20of%20its%20practices%20rooted%20in%20caste-based%20societal%20division%20and%20oppression.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20proponents%20of%20sanatan%20dharma%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fcurrent-affairs%2F050923%2Fayodhya-seer-issues-death-threat-to-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatan-dh.html%5C%22%3Epromulgated%20death%20threats%20against%20Udhayanidhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20twisted%20his%20arguments%20claiming%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstpost.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-udhayanidhis-genocidal-statement-smacks-of-stalinist-terror-and-is-both-dangerous-and-ahistorical-13075462.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20called%20for%20a%20genocide%20and%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0circulated%20videos%20of%20Hindu%20devotees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Findore%2Findore-watch-hindu-jagran-manch-use-udhayanidhis-picture-as-doormat-outside-temple-crush-it-with-feet-to-protest-his-remarks-on-sanatan-dharma%5C%22%3Estomping%20on%20his%20photos%20used%20as%20doormats%20in%20front%20of%20temples.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Learned%20ministers%20mocked%20him%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fyou-dont-have-right-say-union-finance-minister-udhayanidhi-stalins-sanatana-dharma-remark-2436718-2023-09-17%5C%22%3Enot%20calling%20out%20other%20religions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20None%20of%20these%20chosen%20methods%20really%20explain%20to%20us%20what%20is%20it%20in%20their%20sanatan%20dharma%20that%20they%20are%20proud%20of.%20How%20is%20Udhayanidhi%20wrong%20in%20proclaiming%20his%20stand%20of%20working%20towards%20eradication%20of%20a%20dharma%20that%20is%20divisive%20to%20the%20core%3F%20Criticising%20sanatan%20dharma%20is%20by%20no%20means%20an%20endorsement%20of%20regressive%20measures%20adopted%20by%20other%20religions.%20This%20happens%20to%20be%20our%20concern%20because%20it%20affects%20millions%20that%20live%20amongst%20us.%20If%20the%20followers%20of%20the%20said%20dharma%20are%20supporters%20of%20birth-based%20caste%20demarcation%20and%20discrimination%2C%20they%20should%20state%20their%20stance%20rather%20than%20rabble-rouse.%20If%20their%20allegiance%20is%20to%20an%20inequitable%20system%20designed%20to%20benefit%20a%20few%20and%20oppress%20the%20many%20rather%20than%20to%20a%20Constitution%20that%20treats%20all%20as%20equals%2C%20then%20they%20should%20come%20clean%20about%20it.%20Rather%20than%20venerate%20Ambedkar%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20thwart%20the%20constitution%20at%20every%20available%20opportunity%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Fnation%2Freligious-rituals-during-new-parliament-inauguration-show-country-being-taken-backwards-says-sharad-pawar%5C%22%3Eperforming%20religious%20rites%20in%20the%20Parliament%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-has-gone-from-dog-whistle-to-vulture-politics%5C%22%3Edog-whistling%20against%20religious%20minorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20election%20rallies%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20should%20declare%20that%20his%20allegiance%20to%20sanatan%20dharma%20is%20overarching.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanatan%20Dharma%3A%20An%20Ideology%20or%20the%20Entire%20Hindu%20Community%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsanatan-dharma-an-ideology-or-the-entire-hindu-community%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Dharma%3A%20An%20Ideology%20or%20the%20Entire%20Hindu%20Community%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20already%20made%20evident%2C%20this%20debate%2C%20however%2C%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20Modi%20himself.%20Even%20though%20the%20BJP%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20mantle%20of%20protector%20of%20sanatan%20dharma%20today%2C%20social%20reformers%20and%20thought%20leaders%20have%20battled%20much%20mightier%20foes.%20In%20fact%2C%20one%20might%20even%20argue%20that%20soft%20Hindutva%20is%20much%20more%20of%20a%20threat%20by%20not%20speaking%20up%20against%20the%20subjugation%20in-built%20in%20sanatan%20dharma%20and%20in%20many%20ways%20has%20therefore%20become%20a%20precursor%20to%20hard%20Hindutva.%20Years%20of%20such%20a%20soft%20Hindutva%20approach%20that%20chooses%20to%20remain%20silent%20in%20the%20face%20of%20crass%20discrimination%20has%20only%20pushed%20more%20and%20more%20gullible%20masses%20into%20the%20fold%20of%20sanatan%20dharma%20%E2%80%93%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20today%20many%20of%20them%20fail%20to%20recognise%20that%20they%20are%20the%20oppressed%20and%20have%20rather%20become%20the%20foot-soldiers%20of%20hard%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sad%20reality%20that%20opponents%20of%20sanatan%20dharma%20today%20are%20having%20to%20fight%20the%20same%20pitched%20battles%20that%20were%20once%20fought%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Asoka%20the%20great%20more%20than%202%2C000%20years%20ago.%20That%20shows%20the%20staying%20power%20of%20regressive%20social%20practices.%20It%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20society%20that%20we%20live%20in%20that%20is%20still%20mired%20in%20the%20stench%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20proclaiming%20success%20over%20sending%20spaceships%20to%20the%20moon.%20Nevertheless%2C%20whether%20scripted%20or%20not%2C%20remarks%20by%20Udhayanidhi%20have%20brought%20the%20much%20needed%20limelight%20on%20to%20this%20topic%20that%20is%20the%20bane%20of%20our%20existence%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20tackled%20head%20on%20if%20India%20is%20to%20ever%20move%20on%20to%20the%20progressive%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EG.%20Naveen%20is%20a%20Telugu%20physician%20by%20profession%20and%20rationalist%20by%20passion.%20His%20articles%20are%20devoted%20towards%20voicing%20the%20concerns%20of%20downtrodden%20and%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695173430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19154928%2Fabhijeet-gou