%20action%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20including%20the%20killing%20of%20popular%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPro-Khalistani%20outfits%20such%20as%20the%20World%20Sikh%20Organization%20(WSO)%2C%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%2C%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20(SFJ)%20and%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20(BKI)%2C%20working%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20been%20allegedly%20operating%20freely%20from%20the%20Canadian%20soil%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAllegations%20levelled%20against%20India%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20and%20politicians%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20and%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20are%20incorrect%20and%20based%20on%20unsubstantiated%20assumptions%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20deportations%20of%20wanted%20terrorists%20and%20gangsters%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20Indian%20authorities%20at%20multiple%20diplomatic%20and%20security%20talks%20but%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20remained%20non-committal%20and%20brazen%20in%20support%20of%20these%20terror%20elements%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultiple%20dossiers%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Canadian%20side%20but%20India's%20deportation%20requests%20have%20gone%20unaddressed%2C%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20at%20least%20nine%20separatist%20organisations%20supporting%20terror%20groups%20have%20found%20their%20bases%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEight%20individuals%20involved%20in%20terror%20activities%20and%20as%20many%20gangsters%2C%20who%20have%20been%20conspiring%20with%20Pakistan's%20spy%20agency%20ISI%2C%20have%20found%20a%20safe%20haven%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeportation%20requests%20for%20these%20people%20-%20including%20Gurwant%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20early%201990s%20-%20have%20been%20pending%20with%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20for%20years%20now%2C%20they%20said.%20An%20Interpol%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20is%20also%20pending%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20Indian%20authorities%20had%20requested%20for%20the%20deportation%20of%20Gurpreet%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20involved%20in%20terror%20cases%2C%20and%20provided%20his%20Canadian%20address%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20request%20for%20deportation%20of%20dreaded%20gangsters%20including%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20alias%20Arsh%20Dalla%2C%20wanted%20in%2016%20criminal%20cases%2C%20Satinderjit%20Singh%20Brar%20alias%20Goldy%20Brar%2C%20who%20took%20responsibility%20for%20killing%20of%20famous%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%2C%20had%20been%20submitted%20with%20evidence%20against%20them%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20separatist%20organisation%20were%20openly%20issuing%20assassination%20threats%2C%20fuelling%20separatist%20agenda%20and%20carrying%20out%20targeted%20killings%20in%20India%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20pointed%20out%20that%20high-profile%20assassination%20of%20popular%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20by%20the%20Canada-based%20gangster%20with%20affiliations%20to%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20Canada-based%20wanted%20terrorists%20are%20Gurwant%20Singh%20Bath%20of%20the%20Dashmesh%20regiment%20of%20Khalistan%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Brar%20(who%20is%20son%20of%20Pakistan-based%20terrorist%20Lakhbeer%20Singh%20Rhode)%2C%20Moninder%20Singh%20Bual%2C%20Satinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20carried%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Punjab%20on%20November%2010%2C%201977%20and%20was%20affiliated%20with%20the%20now%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF).%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20mid%201990s.%20He%20managed%20to%20get%20bail%20and%20fled%20India%20on%20February%2019%2C%201997%20by%20assuming%20a%20fake%20identity%20of%20Ravi%20Sharma%20and%20securing%20a%20travel%20document%20in%20that%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202013-14%2C%20Nijjar%20visited%20Pakistan%20where%20he%20met%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara%20of%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%2C%20wanted%20in%20assassination%20of%20Punjab%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Beant%20Singh.%20He%20was%20during%20that%20period%20roped%20in%20by%20the%20ISI%20which%20helped%20him%20in%20organising%20secret%20training%20camps%20for%20Sikh%20extremist%20groups%20associated%20with%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20in%20Missigen%20Hills%2C%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20working%20closely%20with%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20(BKI)%20led%20by%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara.%20He%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Dal%20Khalsa%20leader%20Gajender%20Singh%2C%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20hijacking%20of%20an%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20in%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20name%20figured%20in%20the%20most%20wanted%20list%20handed%20over%20by%20then%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Captain%20Amrinder%20Singh%20to%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20along%20with%20criminals%20like%20Arsh%20Dalla%20were%20generating%20huge%20amounts%20of%20funds%20for%20anti-India%20activities%20by%20various%20means%20which%20included%20drug%20money%20and%20finances%20from%20Gurdwaras%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Canada's%20current%20diplomatic%20standoff%20with%20India%20appears%20to%20be%20motivated%20by%20failures%20on%20the%20domestic%20political%20front%20and%20declining%20popularity%20of%20the%20present%20government%20and%20expulsion%20of%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20seems%20to%20be%2