rvation%20Bill%20that%20seeks%20to%20provide%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20in%20the%20ongoing%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20discussion%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20the%20House%20will%20meet%20at%2011%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Cabinet%20on%20Monday%20approved%20the%20Women%20Reservation%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20introduced%20the%20bill%20in%20the%20first%20sitting%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20The%20bill%20has%20been%20named%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20UPA%20government%20tabled%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20and%20it%20was%20passed%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20never%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntroducing%20the%20bill%20in%20the%20house%20Meghawal%20said%20%26quot%3BThis%20bill%20is%20in%20relation%20to%20women%20empowerment.%20By%20amending%20Article%20239AA%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%2033%20per%20cent%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20(NCT)%20of%20Delhi.%20Article%20330A%20reservations%20of%20seats%20for%20SC%2FST%20in%20the%20House%20of%20People.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArjun%20Meghwal%20also%20said%20that%20once%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20is%20passed%2C%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20increase%20to%20181.%20Discussion%20for%20passing%20of%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20House%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2020.%20The%20Bill%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20September%2021%20government%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20