hing%20centre%20for%20abetting%20suicide%20after%20the%20girl's%20father%20claimed%20the%20institute%20was%20%26quot%3Bharassing%20her%26quot%3B%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkota-institute-was-harassing-her-father-of-teen-who-died-by-suicide-4404732%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tests%20Carried%20Out%20On%20Mexico's%20'Alien%20Bodies'%3A%20''No%20Evidence%20Of%20Any...''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoctors%20in%20Mexico%20City%20have%20conducted%20extensive%20laboratory%20studies%20on%20the%20two%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%26quot%3B%20alien%20corpses%20revealed%20last%20week.%20The%20tests%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20Jose%20de%20Jesus%20Zalce%20Benitez%2C%20a%20forensic%20doctor%20with%20the%20navy%20at%20the%20Noor%20Clinic%20on%20Monday%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-66853551%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr.%20Benitez%20concluded%20that%20the%20so-called%20bodies%20belonged%20to%20a%20single%20skeleton%20and%20were%20not%20assembled.%20He%C2%A0also%20said%20that%20the%20laboratory%20tests%20have%20shown%20that%20''there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20assembly%20or%20manipulation%20of%20the%20skulls''.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-mysterious-non-human-alien-corpses-displayed-at-mexicos-congress-4386001%5C%22%3E%20mummies%20were%20presented%20by%20Jaime%20Maussan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20speculated%20widely%20on%20aliens.%20The%20mysterious%20bodies%20are%20tiny%20in%20stature%20and%20chalky%20in%20colour%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20them%20has%20three-fingered%20hands%20and%20shrunken%20heads.%C2%A0One%20was%20described%20as%20female%2C%20with%20eggs%20inside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20specimens%20were%20