2%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TDP%20Sets%20Up%20Website%20to%20Counter%20Skill%20Development%20Scheme%20Charges%2C%20Highlights%20Praise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09104128%2FF5jlMjCaUAAGVIz.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20the%20political%20slugfest%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20over%20former%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20early%20on%20September%209%20morning%20continues%2C%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20on%20Tuesday%20set%20up%20a%20website%20that%20it%20claims%20reveals%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20alleged%20skilled%20development%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunching%20the%20website%2C%20apskilldevelopmenttruth.com%2C%20state%20TDP%20president%20Kinjarapu%20Atchannaidu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20easily%20understand%20how%20Chandrababu%20perfectly%20designed%20the%20project%20to%20take%20the%20youth%20to%20greater%20heights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20party%20would%20put%20forth%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%20every%20day%20and%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20corruption%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20details%20that%20the%20website%20lists%20is%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20established%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20numbers%20of%20clusters%20and%20trained%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%20among%20all%20the%20states%20that%20had%20similar%20schemes.%20After%20AP%20started%20the%20project%2C%20other%20states%20started%20emulating%20the%20hub%20and%20set%20up%20training%20centres%2C%20the%20website%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20was%20also%20ranked%20first%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20India%20Skills%20Report%202018%20and%202019%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20then%20TDP%20government%2C%20the%20website%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaidu%20was%20arrested%20at%20RK%20Function%20Hall%20in%20Nandyal%20on%20September%2019.%20According%20to%20the%20AP%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%2C%20the%20case%20against%20Naidu%20and%20others%20involves%20funds%20allegedly%20being%20routed%20through%20hawala%20transactions%20through%20a%20network%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20non-adherence%20to%20procedures%2C%20a%20disregard%20for%20observations%20regarding%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20viability%2C%20and%20the%20questioning%20of%20over%20140%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20alleged%20scam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20murky%20deal%20revolves%20around%20the%20AP%20State%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(APSSDC)%2C%20a%20government%20agency%20established%20shortly%20after%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20secured%20victory%20in%20the%20elections%20in%202014.%20It%20also%20involves%20Siemens%20Industry%20Software%20(India)%20Pvt%20Limited%20and%20DesignTech%20Systems%20Pvt%20Limited%2C%20a%20Pune-based%20company%20tasked%20with%20supporting%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CID%20described%20Naidu%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprincipal%20architect%20of%20the%20scheme%E2%80%9D.%20They%20contend%20that%20the%20APSSDC%20was%20formed%20without%20the%20state%20Cabinet%E2%80%99s%20nod.%20Naidu%2C%20the%20CID%20claimed%2C%20along%20with%20then%20minister%20K.%20Atchannaidu%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfraudulently%E2%80%9D%20projected%20to%20the%20AP%20government%20that%20the%20two%20companies%20would%20support%20the%20project%2C%20work%20to%20create%20six%20centres%20of%20excellence%20(CoE)%20and%2036%20technical%20skill%20development%20institutes.%20All%20of%20this%20was%20to%20be%20achieved%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20around%20Rs%203%2C281%20crore.%20The%20CID%20claims%20that%20this%20is%20an%20inflated%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20state%20was%20to%20invest%2010%25%20of%20this%20cost%2C%20the%20remaining%2090%25%20would%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20grants-in-aid%20from%20the%20two%20companies.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20established%20the%20Skill%20Development%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Innovation%20Department.%20In%20an%20apparent%20effort%20to%20exercise%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20skilling%20project%20and%20avoid%20bureaucratic%20oversight%2C%20Naidu%20allegedly%20designated%20the%20APSSDC%20as%20an%20agency%20within%20this%20department.%20It%20was%20noted%20that%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20who%20is%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20Siemens%20director%2C%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20APSSDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CID%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20agreement%2C%20a%20tripartite%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20(MOU)%20was%20prepared%20with%20a%20clause%20stipulating%20that%20the%20AP%20government%20would%20release%20Rs%20371%20crore%20as%20a%20grant%20to%20Siemens%20and%20DesignTech%20to%20set%20up%20skill%20development%20institutes.%20The%20CID%20remand%20report%20of%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20submitted%20before%20the%20special%20judge%20for%20SPE%20and%20ACB%20cases%20in%20Vijayawada%20notes%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20project%20which%20was%20conceived%20to%20be%20primarily%20funded%20to%20the%20extent%20of%2090%25%20by%20Siemens%20and%20DesignTech%20was%20illegally%20converted%20into%20a%20full%20government-funded%20project%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CID%20alleges%20that%20the%20Rs%20371%20crore%20was%20disbursed%20to%20DesignTech%20even%20before%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20skill%20development%20institutes.%20It%20further%20accuses%20staff%20members%20of%20both%20Siemens%20and%20DesignTech%20of%20misappropriating%20these%20funds.%20The%20remand%20report%20dedicates%20a%20significant%20portion%20to%20file%20notations%2C%20with%20particular%20emphasis%20on%20the%20notations%20made%20by%20certain%20civil%20servants%20who%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20releasing%20funds%20to%20DesignTech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20came%20as%20a%20double%20whammy%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20too%20launched%20a%20probe%20over%20money%20laundering.%20It%20provisionally%20attached%20properties%20belonging%20to%20DesignTech%20worth%20Rs%2031.20%20crore%20and%20previously%20arrested%20Siemens%E2%80%99%20former%20managing%20director%20Soumyadri%20Shekhar%20Bose%2C%20DesignTech%E2%80%99s%20managing%20director%20Vikas%20Vinayak%20Khanvelkar%2C%20former%20financial%20advisor%20to%20Skillar%20Ent%20Mukul%20Chandra%20Agrawal%20and%20Suresh%20Goyal.%20The%20Income%20Tax%20Investigation%20wing%20in%20Mumbai%20also%20launched%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20is%20said%20to%20have%20revealed%20that%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20279%20crore%20was%20misappropriated%20through%20shell%20companies.%20These%20allegedly%20did%20no%20work%20and%20raised%20%E2%80%9Cbogus%20invoices%E2%80%9D%2C%20routed%20through%20entities%20and%20individuals.%20Per%20the%20CID%2C%20of%20the%20Rs%20371%20crore%2C%20Siemens%20received%20only%20Rs%2058.80%20crore%20from%20DesignTech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBose%2C%20a%20key%20accused%20who%20was%20arrested%2C%20recently%20sought%20to%20rubbish%20the%20case%20before%20the%20media%20and%20described%20the%20developments%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20conjecture.%20He%20maintained%20that%20the%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Tool%20Design%20vetted%20the%20project%20and%20there%20was%20appreciation%20for%20the%20project.%20Bose%20claimed%20that%20despite%20there%20being%20no%20scandal%2C%20charges%20were%20framed%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20day%20prior%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20broke%20his%20silence%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20and%20underscored%20that%20the%20ED%20had%20thrown%20light%20on%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement.%20Investigation%20showed%2C%20Reddy%20said%2C%20that%20the%20former%20CM%E2%80%99s%20signatures%20were%20available%20on%20several%20files.%20Attacking%20Naidu%2C%20Reddy%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20t