re%20digital%20rights%20have%20become%20an%20issue%20of%20public%20curiosity%20since%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20participate%20primarily%20in%20English%20and%20some%20Hindi%20debates%20as%20a%20legal%20expert.%20While%20it%20boosted%20my%20public%20recognition%2C%20what%20I%20cherished%20most%20was%20the%20opportunity%20to%20explain%20technical%20nuances%20around%20topics%20like%20web%20censorship%20or%20mass%20surveillance%20to%20a%20broader%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20observed%20a%20concerning%20trend.%20In%202021%2C%20various%20analyses%2C%20including%20those%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F06%2F25%2Ftv-newsance-176-the-data-on-job-debates-studio-veers-dont-want-you-to-know%5C%22%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20highlighted%20a%20not%20only%20decline%20in%20journalistic%20standards%2C%20but%20open%20and%20virulent%20bigotry%20against%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20Faced%20with%20this%20reality%2C%20I%20made%20a%20conscious%20decision%20to%20stop%20appearing%20on%20specific%20television%20channels%2C%20starting%20with%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20never%20saw%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%20TV%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20truth%20or%20journalism%2C%20so%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20compelled%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20announcement%20regarding%20them.%20But%20for%20those%20who%20still%20do%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20furnish%20two%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhpuniv.ac.in%2Fhpuniv%2Fupload%2Fuploadfiles%2Ffiles%2FHPUJ-June-2022-issue.pdf%23page%3D110%5C%22%3Equantitative%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ashish%20Sharma%20and%20Sandeep%20Kumar%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAlthough%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ERepublic%20TV%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98s%20debates%20haven%E2%80%99t%20covered%20any%20pressing%20issues%20that%20affect%20society%2C%20such%20as%20the%20economy%2C%20education%2C%20employment%2C%20or%20health%20conditions.%20Instead%2C%20they%20primarily%20focus%20on%20the%20core%20issue%20of%20politics%20which%20mostly%20attacks%20the%20opposition%20and%20any%20group%20or%20individuals%20opposing%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20ruling%20government.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Ashwini%20Ramesh%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FRijitha-R%2Fpublication%2F358730635_THE_IMPACT_OF_SOCIAL_MEDIA_MARKETING_ON_CONSUMER_PURCHASE_INTENTION%2Flinks%2F63f725205749505945377a51%2FTHE-IMPACT-OF-SOCIAL-MEDIA-MARKETING-ON-CONSUMER-PURCHASE-INTENTION.pdf%23page%3D26%5C%22%3Ecrunched%20the%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20comparative%20assessment%20holds%20that%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRepublic%20TV%3Cem%3E%20involves%20in%20media%20framing%20the%20most%20as%20compared%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndia%20Today%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3ENDTV%2024%C3%977%3Cem%3E%20news%20channels.%20Conflict%20and%20anti-journalistic%20objectivity%20frames%20are%20the%20most%20popular%20frames%20for%20prime-time%20television%20debates%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20if%20these%20choices%20have%20been%20easy%20or%20certain.%20Even%20before%202021%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%20concerning%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20during%20Faye%20D%E2%80%99Souza%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20at%20%3Cem%3EMirror%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20halt%20my%20appearances%20there%20due%20to%20no%20fault%20of%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FbBNk4YLkECM%3Fsi%3DABsnw-IpqKzxdvYC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20period%20when%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20targeted%20civil%20society%20activists%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20labelling%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20for%20their%20dissenting%20views.%20Selective%20facts%20from%20their%20public%20and%20personal%20lives%20were%20unveiled%2C%20accompanied%20by%20doctored%20videos%20and%20unfair%20characterisations%2C%20creating%20public%20turmoil%20and%20eroding%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20these%20broadcasts%20resulted%20in%20real-world%20harm%2C%20including%20criminal%20prosecutions%2C%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20homes%20for%20many%20individuals.%20I%20grappled%20with%20internal%20moral%20considerations%2C%20as%20the%20progressive%20broadcast%20by%20%3Cem%3EMirror%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20the%20Times%20Group%2C%20which%20also%20operated%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20recall%20the%20exact%20decision-making%20process%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20increase%20my%20contributions%20to%20national%20newspapers%20by%20shifting%20time%20from%20TV%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20about%20certain%20newspapers%20advancing%20a%20majoritarian%20agenda%2C%20there%20was%20a%20marked%20difference%20between%20them%20and%20late-night%20primetime%20shows.%20Concerns%2C%20if%20any%2C%20were%20more%20subtle%20and%20mostly%20on%20themes%20of%20neoliberalism%20and%20market-based%20interventions.%20Here%2C%20I%20continue%20to%20benefit%20from%20these%20platforms%20for%20professional%20growth%20through%20increased%20visibility%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20publish%20commentary%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20public%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20in%20complete%20political%20and%20moral%20agreement%2C%20but%20refuse%20to%20be%20an%20accessory%20to%20a%20media%20entity%20directing%20threats%20and%20hate%20speech.%20Through%20these%20instances%2C%20I%20maintained%20a%20clear%20boundary%20%E2%80%93%20I%20steadfastly%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20debates%20hosted%20by%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fapar1984%2Fstatus%2F1702992257996255301%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ereiterated%20my%20stance%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20addition.%20I%20believe%20that%20not%20only%20should%20more%20experts%20and%20panellists%20be%20deliberate%20in%20their%20choice%20of%20anchors%20and%20television%20platforms%2C%20but%20also%20make%20it%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20Call%20for%20Boycott%20of%20Newspapers%20Spreading%20Hatred%20Resonates%20With%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETransparency%20serves%20their%20own%20ethical%20obligations%20but%20also%20fosters%20greater%20accountability%20towards%20themselves%20and%20broadcasters.%20This%20is%20not%20mere%20%E2%80%9Cvirtue%20signalling%E2%80%9D%3B%20for%20many%2C%20it%20will%20entail%20a%20cost%2C%20as%20it%20means%20forgoing%20airtime%20and%20opportunities%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20personal%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20such%20public%20declarations%20may%20not%20be%20flawless%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20reduce%20inconsistencies%20and%20build%20solidarity.%20Inevitably%2C%20private%20individuals%20may%20make%20exceptions%20to%20their%20non-participation%20stance%20to%20support%20junior%20journalists%20or%20address%20issues%20of%20strategic%20or%20emotional%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20public%20statements%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20check%20against%20undue%20compromise.%20I%20acknowledge%20that%20I%20am%20not%20the%20first%20to%20make%20this%20call%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20that%20more%20voices%20taking%20this%20step%20and%20repeatedly%20stating%20it%20in%20public%20is%20a%20meaningful%20contribution%20towards%20the%20restoration%20of%20consti