20by%20the%20opposition.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20a%20political%20slugfest%2C%20with%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CEmergency%E2%80%9D%20mindset%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20while%20Congress%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cnon-cooperation%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cboycott%E2%80%9D%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOn%20the%20same%20issue%2C%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%20interviewed%20veteran%20journalist%20and%20former%20editor-in-chief%20and%20publisher%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Hindu%3Cem%3E%2C%20N.%20Ram%2C%20on%20September%2015.%20The%20interview%20looks%20at%20the%20boycott%20call%20given%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20from%20a%20critical%20view%2C%20covering%20different%20aspects%20and%20implications%20of%20such%20a%20move.%20How%20fair%20is%20it%20to%20single%20out%20individual%20anchors%20while%20letting%20television%20channels%20go%20scot-free%20assuming%20that%20hate%20is%20being%20propagated%20by%20certain%20anchors%20on%20their%20shows%3F%20What%20is%20the%20political%20message%20behind%20drawing%20up%20such%20a%20list%3F%20Does%20it%20actually%20serve%20a%20purpose%3F%20Would%20it%20have%20been%20better%20for%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis%2C%20like%20turning%20down%20offers%20to%20appear%20on%20such%20shows%2C%20rather%20than%20come%20up%20with%20a%20list%3F%20What%20does%20it%20indicate%20about%20the%20state%20of%20Indian%20journalism%3F%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20many%20questions%20and%20angles%20that%20are%20part%20of%20this%2035-minute%20interview.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20the%20full%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style%2C%20clarity%20and%20syntax.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%E2%80%99s%20(INDIA%20alliance)%20decision%20to%20boycott%2014%20television%20anchors%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20identified%20by%20name%20has%20created%20a%20storm%20of%20controversy.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20my%20intention%20to%20examine%20several%20aspects%20of%20this%20decision%2C%20and%20joining%20me%20for%20the%20discussion%20is%20a%20man%20that%20many%20people%20consider%20India%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20journalist%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20the%20doyen%20of%20our%20profession%2C%20the%20former%20editor-in-chief%20and%20publisher%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20N.%20Ram.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMr.%20Ram%2C%20I%20want%20to%20raise%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%2014%20television%20anchors%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20identified%20by%20name.%20But%20let%20me%20first%20start%20with%20what%20I%20would%20call%20a%20moral%20concern%3A%20Is%20it%20fitting%20in%20a%20democracy%20for%20politicians%20to%20boycott%20fellow%20citizens%3F%20Is%20there%20not%20something%20distasteful%2C%20or%20even%20unethical%2C%20about%20boycotting%20fellow%20human%20beings%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaran%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20pleasure%20and%20an%20educational%20experience%20talking%20to%20you.%20This%20is%20more%20a%20conversation%20than%20an%20interview%20%E2%80%93%20I%20take%20that%20for%20granted%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that%20first.%20As%20a%20starting%20point%2C%20I%20would%20agree%20that%20those%20in%20politics%20and%20public%20affairs%20should%20be%20accessible%20%E2%80%93%20not%20that%20all%20of%20them%20are%20and%20the%20man%20right%20at%20the%20top%20is%20not%20really%20accessible%20in%20the%20way%20previous%20prime%20ministers%20are.%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20I%20would%20agree%20with%20the%20starting%20point%2C%20but%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20journalists%20or%20anchor