20the%20controversy%20of%20a%20boycott.%20It%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20a%20very%20easy%20option%2C%20they%20could%E2%80%99ve%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20will%20not%20accept%20invitations%20of%20anchors%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%E2%80%99%2C%20rather%20than%20go%20public%20and%20announce%20a%20boycott%20and%20attract%20controversy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20interesting%20point.%20I%20must%20tell%20you%20that%20just%20before%20we%20had%20this%20conversation%2C%20I%20had%20several%20journalists%20here%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Chennai%20Press%20Club%20trying%20to%20revive%20it%20because%20there%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20elections%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20there%20are%20about%20a%20dozen%20people%2C%20including%20well-known%20names%20in%20media%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20So%20I%20took%20advantage%20of%20that%20meeting%20to%20have%20been%20something%20else%2C%20to%20pull%20the%20group.%20It%20included%20people%20like%20Nakkheeran%20Gopal%2C%20Bhagawan%20Singh%2C%20veteran%20journalists%20as%20well%20as%20young%20journalists%20Kavita%20Muralidharan%20and%20so%20on.%20Without%20exception%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%2C%20they%20said%20this%20was%20the%20right%20answer%20but%20one%20of%20them%20said%20exactly%20what%20you%20said%20%E2%80%93%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20sort%20of%20making%20an%20announcement%2C%20you%20just%20made%20a%20decision%20not%20to%20accept%20invitations%20from%20those%20anchors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3EIndia%20Alliance%20to%20Boycott%20TV%20Shows%20That%20%E2%80%98Conduct%20Inflammatory%20Debates%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20against%20it%2C%20the%20others%20said%3B%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20quite%20interesting%2C%20we%20spoke%20for%20about%2010-15%20minutes%20on%20