llegation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19140300%2FF6XA2MyWQAAYBoQ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20son%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20Sikh%20leader%20killed%20in%20June%20this%20year%20in%20Canada%2C%20said%20his%20family%20had%20always%20suspected%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20behind%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20killing%2C%20asking%20the%20Canadian%20government%20to%20take%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20a%20step%20further%E2%80%9D%20to%20identify%20specific%20individuals%20who%20may%20have%20been%20involved%20and%20place%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Fslain-bc-sikh-leader-son-1.6971081%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20CBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20public%20broadcaster%2C%20Balraj%20Singh%20Nijjar%20said%20he%20felt%20a%20%E2%80%9Csense%20of%20relief%E2%80%9D%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20involved%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20He%20was%20speaking%20publicly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20killing%20of%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20for%20when%20the%20truth%20would%20come%20out%E2%80%A6%20When%20we%20heard%20the%20news%20today%2C%20it%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20finally%20coming%20to%20the%20public%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHopefully%2C%20you%20can%20take%20this%20a%20step%20further%20and%20get%20specific%20individuals%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20place%20sanctions%2C%20whatever%20the%20next%20steps%20are%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20waiting%20as%20a%20family%20to%20see%20what%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20addressing%20Canadian%20leaders%2C%20according%20to%20CBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20British%20Columbia%20(B.C.)%20asked%20for%20%E2%80%9Cbetter%20protection%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20community%20hours%20after%20Trudeau%20alleged%20India%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENijjar%20headed%20the%20pro-Khalistan%20outfits%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20the%20Canadian%20arm%20of%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ).%20He%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20B.C.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20wanted%20for%20the%20shooting%20of%20a%20priest%20in%20Punjab%20and%20was%20the%20third%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20to%20die%20abroad%20in%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half.%20Immediately%20after%20his%20death%2C%20his%20supporters%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20behind%20the%20killing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorld%20Sikh%20Organisation%20president%20Tejinder%20Singh%20Sidhu%20said%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20vindicated%20those%20who%20have%20%E2%80%9Clong%20accused%20India%20of%20targeting%20Canadian%20Sikhs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Canada%20has%20publicly%20said%20what%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%20have%20known%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20India%20actively%20targets%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20should%20now%20be%20clear%20to%20all%20Canadians%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20a%20terrorist%20state%20that%20has%20brazenly%20engaged%20in%20extrajudicial%20killings%20not%20only%20on%20its%20own%20soil%2C%20but%20also%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2F