ird%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20be%20occupied%20by%20women%20will%20be%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20the%20Bill%20says%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprovisions%20relating%20to%20the%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20%E2%80%A6%20shall%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20an%20exercise%20of%20delimitation%20is%20undertaken%20for%20this%20purpose%20after%20the%20relevant%20figures%20for%20the%20first%20census%20taken%20after%20%5Bthe%20Bill%20is%20passed%5D%20have%20been%20published.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20provision%20trying%20reservation%20to%20a%20fresh%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2008%2FWomen_Reservation_Bill_as_passed_on_Mar_9.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20not%20part%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20effectively%20postpones%20the%20actual%20implementation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D%20measure%20to%20some%20unspecified%20date%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20for%20the%202021%20census%20was%20postponed%20in%202020%20%E2%80%93%20ostensibly%20due%20to%20Covid%20%E2%80%93%20and%20no%20new%20date%20for%20its%20commencement%20has%20yet%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssuming%20the%20census%20is%20held%20some%20time%20after%20the%202024%20election%2C%20its%20results%20would%20take%20a%20year%20to%20compile%20and%20publish%2C%20after%20which%20an%20unspecified%20delimitation%20exercise%20would%20then%20have%20to%20be%20undertaken.%20Even%20though%20this%20work%20could%20conceivably%20be%20completed%20within%20a%20year%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20reservation%20would%20only%20kick%20in%20after%20the%20existing%20house%20is%20dissolved%20%E2%80%93%20presumably%20after%20its%20five%20year%20term%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20assembly%20elections%20could%20conceivably%20be%20held%20under%20the%20new%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20speech%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20days%20which%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cmilestones%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20history%20of%20every%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20milestones%20come%20in%20the%20development%20journey%20of%20every%20country%2C%20when%20it%20proudly%20says%20that%20today%20we%20have%20created%20a%20new%20history.%20In%20the%20first%20speech%20of%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20new%20House%2C%20I%20am%20saying%20with%20great%20confidence%20and%20pride%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20moment%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20day%20is%20going%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%20minutes%20prior%20to%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20listed%20The%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20be%20introduced%20by%20Meghwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F672226424%2FWomen-s-Reservation-Bill-2023%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%202023%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F672226424%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-unC45LtgNdqhZ9n8iNeI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7080062794348508%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%202023%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20speculation%20surrounding%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20legislation%20after%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20on%20Monday%20reportedly%20cleared%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20granting%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20no%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20government.%20There%20was%20also%20no%20cabinet%20briefing%20after%20the%20meeting%20late%20on%20Monday%2C%20which%20usually%20takes%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20while%20there%20have%20been%20several%20attempts%20in%20the%20past%20to%20get%20this%20legislation%20passed%2C%20they%20were%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20pride%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20For%20several%20years%2C%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20has%20been%20discussed%20in%20parliament.%20This%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%201996.%20During%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20era%2C%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20presented%20several%20times%20but%20numbers%20were%20not%20enough%20to%20get%20it%20passed%20so%20that%20dream%20remained%20unfulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20I%20have%20been%20chosen%20by%20God%20to%20do%20this%20auspicious%20work.%20Once%20again%20our%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20step%20in%20this%20direction.%20In%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20approved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20urged%20all%20parliament%20members%20to%20build%20consensus%20and%20pass%20the%20Bill%20upon%20its%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E33%20percent%20reservation%20to%20lapse%20after%2015%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20states%20that%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20by%20amending%20Article%20239AA%2C%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20amending%20Article%20330%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20and%20one-third%20seats%20reserved%20in%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20by%20amending%20Article%20332.%20The%20Bill%20will%20be%20named%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20currently%20reserved%20or%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Schedule%20Tribes%20will%20also%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20from%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20also%20has%20a%20built-in%20sunset%20provision%20of%2015%20years%20%E2%80%93%20after%20which%20reservation%20for%20women%20will%20automatically%20lapse.%20Unless%2C%20of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20renewed%20by%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons%2C%20the%20Bill%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20enable%20greater%20participation%20of%20women%20as%20public%20representative%20in%20policy%20making%20at%20State%20and%20national%20level%2C%20it%20is%20decided%20to%20introduce%20a%20fresh%20legislation%20for%20Constitutional%20amendment%20to%20provide%20for%2C%20as%20nearly%2C%20as%20may%20be%2C%20one-third%20of%20total%20seats%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20every%20State%20and%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20to%20be%20reserved%20for%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202008%20%E2%80%93%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20and%20passed%20by%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20fierce%20opposition%20from%20a%20few%20political%20parties%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20never%20pursued%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECredit%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20protests%20were%20raised%20from%20the%20Treasury%20benches%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%20that%20successive%20Congress%20governments%20beginning%20with%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20had%20sought%20to%20provide%20reservations%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reservation%20issue%20raised%20by%20the%20PM%20now%2C%20I%20want%20to%20state%2C%20the%20legislation%20was%20brought%20by%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20in%201989%20in%20local%20elections%20with%201%2F3%20reservations%20for%20women.%20Successive%20Congress%20governments%20have%20subsequently%20tried%20to%20get%20the%20Bill%20passed.%20From%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20to%20the%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%20to%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%2C%20different%20Congress%20governments%20at%20different%20times%20have%20tried%20to%20get%20it%20passed.%20If%20it%20was%20passed%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20it%20would%20get%20stuck%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20or%20if%20it%20was%20passed%20by%20Lok%20Sabha%20it%20would%20fall%20through%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bill%20brought%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20still%20valid%20as%20it%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Even%20in%20the%20CWC%20meeting%2C%20we%20demanded%20the%20passage%20of%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20MP%20was%20asked%20to%20conclude%20his%20speech%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20rose%20from%20his%20seat%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20MP%20of%20stating%20%E2%80%9Cincorrect%20facts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdhir%20Ranjan%20ji%20has%20stated%20two%20incorrect%20facts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20he%20should%20withdraw%20his%20comments%20or%20he%20should%20place%20the%20documents%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house.%20First%2C%20that%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20never%20been%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20And%20second%2C%20that%20the%20old%20Bill%20is%20valid%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20Bill%20lapsed%20in%202014.%20He%20has%20made%20two%20factually%20incorrect%20statements.%20He%20should%20be%20asked%20to%20clarify%20or%20his%20statements%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20records%2C%20or%20he%20should%20place%20the%20relevant%20records%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Chaudhary%20concluded%20his%20speech%2C%20Shah%20once%20again%20rose%20to%20reiterate%20the%20same%20points%20amid%20protests%20raised%20by%20the%20opposition%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20session%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20ends%2C%20the%20Bill%20also%20lapses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20Bill%20introduced%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20as%20Meghwal%20rose%20to%20introduce%20the%20Bill%2C%20opposition%20members%20raised%20protests%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20had%20not%20been%20listed%20in%20the%20house%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeghwal%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20has%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20supplementary%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bill%20has%20been%20uploaded%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Meghwal%20amid%20the%20din.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Bill%20had%20only%20been%20listed%20in%20the%20supplementary%20list%20of%20business%20moments%20prior%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20while%20introducing%20the%20Bill%2C%20Meghwal%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20under%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20had%20lapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Bill%20was%20brought%20in%20September%201996%20under%20Deve%20Gowda.%20Then%20in%201998%2C%20the%20Vajpayee%20government%20brought%20it%20and%20then%20again%20in%201999%2C%20the%20Vajpayee%20government%20brought%20it%20again.%20The%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20brought%20it%20in%202008%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20And%20then%20it%20went%20to%20the%20department-related%20standing%20committee%20and%20when%20the%20report%20(from%20the%20committee)%20came%2C%20it%20was%20brought%20and%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Then%20it%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20and%20became%20a%20property%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20When%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha%20ended%2C%20this%20bill%20also%20lapsed.%20And%20these%20people%20did%20not%20pass%20it%20purposely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20din%20in%20the%20house%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20treasury%20benches%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20is%20only%20being%20tabled%20and%20a%20discussion%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20is%20a%20developing%20story%20and%20details%20will%20be%20added%20as%20they%20become%20available.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695114036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19142643%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.18-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistoric-day-says-pm-modi-as-he-announces-womens-reservation-bill-in-new-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20clause%20trying%20reservation%20to%20a%20fresh%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%20and%20effectively%