-virus-dr-anoop-kumar-diagnosis-bats-kozhikode-kerala%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Kept%20Its%20Soul%20Intact%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Kerala%20Architect%20Renovated%20Her%20100-YO%20Home%20With%20Rs%2030%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20between%20cocoa%20plantations%20and%20greenery%20with%20no%20houses%20seen%20within%20a%20mile%2C%20Anupa%20Kurian%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20green%20oasis.%20For%20most%20of%20her%20childhood%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20traditional%20Kottayam-styled%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaced%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314288%2Fkochi-architect-koshy-builds-office-with-discarded-mangalore-tiles-repurposed-wood-steel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangalore%20tiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20the%20house%2C%20as%20per%20Anupa%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20a%20soul%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20intact.%E2%80%9D%20So%20when%20the%20time%20to%20renovate%20the%20100-year-old%20residence%20came%2C%20Anupa%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20knew%20where%20to%20look%20for%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20it%20down%20and%20make%20it%20modern%20but%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247372%2Fkerala-ecofriendly-sustainable-low-cost-home-ashokan-padapelly-fisherman-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20incorporate%20modern%20amenities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20keeping%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20house.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20look%20anywhere%20for%20inspiration%2C%20the%20bones%20and%20structure%20of%20the%20house%20were%20inspiration%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20step%20into%20the%20house%20today%2C%20everything%20a