20to%20bring%20them%20back%20into%20the%20mainstream%20food%20palette%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20their%20products%2C%20there%20are%20only%20three%20steps%20involved%20in%20making%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20you%20crack%20open%20the%20seal%2C%20second%2C%20pour%20water%20as%20per%20your%20requirement%2C%20and%20third%2C%20enjoy%20it%20from%20the%20cup%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20are%20serving%2014%20varieties%20of%20chutneys%20and%20have%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20are%20serving%2014%20varieties%20of%20chutneys%20and%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chutnefy%20Team%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20fathers%2C%20the%20duo%20wanted%20to%20ease%20the%20pressure%20of%20strenuous%20cooking%20off%20of%20their%20wives%2C%20so%20they%20created%20a%20brand%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20time%20consuming.%20The%20brand%