20that%20is%20what%20keeps%20us%20going.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694528347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329731%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prasanna%20Natarajan%20started%20a%20food%20business%20with%20his%20school%20friend%20Shreyas%20Raghav.%20The%20duo%20wanted%20to%20reintroduce%20chutneys%20in%20mainstream%20food%20markets%20and%20take%20them%20outside%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329731%2Fschool-friends-start-a-chutney-business-that-earns-in-lakhs-per-month%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chennai%20Scuba%20Diver%20%26amp%3B%20His%209-YO%20Daughter%20Have%20Collected%201000%20Kg%20Plastic%20From%20The%20Ocean%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20scuba%20diving%20instructor%20by%20profession%2C%20Aravind%20Tharunsri%20has%20been%20cleaning%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ocean%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20collected%2030%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastics%20from%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20advocates%20for%20marine%20conservation%20and%20has%20been%20encouraging%20his%20daughter%20to%20be%20part%20of%20his%20activities.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20joined%20by%20his%20daughter%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20clean%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20daughter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275373%2Fchild-hero-thaaragai-arathana-removes-plastic-waste-from-ocean-scuba-diving%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThaaragai%20Aarathana%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20just%20five%20years%20old%20when%20she%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98543%2Fwater-festival-marine-conservation-india-mumbai%2F%5C%